# ACR Module

This Terraform module creates an Azure Container Registry (ACR) with optional network rules, geo-replications, retention/trust policies, and RBAC role assignments.

## Features

- âś… **ACR Registry** - Create Azure Container Registry with configurable SKU
- âś… **Network Controls** - Public access toggle + IP/subnet allow rules
- âś… **Geo-replication** - Optional cross-region replication (Premium SKU)
- âś… **Registry Policies** - Optional retention, trust, and quarantine policies
- âś… **RBAC Assignments** - Grant AcrPull, AcrPush, and AcrDelete roles
- âś… **Security Defaults** - Managed tags and admin-user toggle
- âś… **Connection Outputs** - Login server + CLI helpers

## Usage

### Call from another repository

Point `source` at this repo and the path under it (`//Azure/ACR`). Pin **`ref` to a tag or commit** in production, not a branch that can change.

```hcl
module "acr" {
  source = "git::https://github.com/saurabhrsahu/terraform-modules.git//Azure/ACR?ref=main"
  # Use ?ref=v1.0.0 (or a commit SHA) once you tag releases
  # ...same inputs as in Basic Usage below
}
```

The **root** module where you call this must configure the **AzureRM** provider and authentication. This module only declares it needs `hashicorp/azurerm`.

```hcl
terraform {
  required_providers {
    azurerm = {
      source  = "hashicorp/azurerm"
      version = ">= 4.0.0, < 5.0.0"
    }
  }
}

provider "azurerm" {
  features {}
}
```

### Basic Usage

```hcl
module "acr" {
  source = "../../modules/Azure/ACR"

  resource_group_name = "rg-platform-dev"
  location            = "eastus"
  acr_name            = "myacrplatformdev01"
  sku                 = "Standard"

  acr_pull_principal_ids = [
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
  ]

  acr_push_principal_ids = [
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
  ]

  tags = {
    team = "platform"
  }
}
```

## Inputs

| Name | Description | Type | Default | Required |
|------|-------------|------|---------|:--------:|
| `resource_group_name` | Resource group for ACR | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `location` | Azure region | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `acr_name` | Container Registry name | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `sku` | ACR SKU (`Basic`, `Standard`, `Premium`) | `string` | `"Standard"` | no |
| `admin_enabled` | Enable admin account | `bool` | `false` | no |
| `public_network_access_enabled` | Enable public network access | `bool` | `true` | no |
| `network_ip_allowlist` | Allowed CIDRs for ACR | `list(string)` | `[]` | no |
| `network_subnet_ids` | Allowed subnet IDs for ACR | `list(string)` | `[]` | no |
| `georeplications` | Geo-replication map (Premium) | `map(object)` | `{}` | no |
| `retention_policy_days` | Untagged retention days (Premium) | `number` | `0` | no |
| `acr_pull_principal_ids` | Principal IDs for AcrPull | `list(string)` | `[]` | no |
| `acr_push_principal_ids` | Principal IDs for AcrPush | `list(string)` | `[]` | no |
| `acr_delete_principal_ids` | Principal IDs for AcrDelete | `list(string)` | `[]` | no |
| `tags` | Additional tags | `map(string)` | `{}` | no |

## Outputs

| Name | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `acr_name` | ACR resource name |
| `acr_id` | ACR resource ID |
| `acr_login_server` | ACR login server |
| `acr_admin_username` | Admin username (if enabled) |
| `acr_admin_password` | Admin password (if enabled, sensitive) |
| `summary` | High-level module summary |
| `connection_info` | CLI and docker helper commands |

## Requirements

| Name | Version |
|------|---------|
| terraform | >= 1.3.0 |
| azurerm | >= 4.0.0, < 5.0.0 |

## Providers

| Name | Version |
|------|---------|
| azurerm | >= 4.0.0, < 5.0.0 |
